/li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://s1.ax1x.com/2023/06/17/pClAg9U.jpg\" alt=\"pClAg9U.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Rebuild</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://s1.ax1x.com/2023/06/17/pClZ91S.png\" alt=\"pClZ91S.png\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<p>可以看到，Rebuild 阶段重排得到了 4 条指令，刚好就是前面提到过的平衡树结构。</p>\n<p>实践中存在更加复杂的例子，如下图所示：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s1.ax1x.com/2023/06/17/pCl9b9J.jpg\" alt=\"pCl9b9J.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<p>UEVar 指活跃变量分析得到的 Use 集合，LiveOut 指活跃变量分析得到的 Out 集合。执行优化变换后的代码如下：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s1.ax1x.com/2023/06/17/pCl957T.jpg\" alt=\"pCl957T.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>参考：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><em>Engineer a Compiler, Second Edition</em></li>\n</ul>\n<p>豆瓣评论：“Keith Cooper人非常好，书也写得不错，酷爱穿花衬衫。”</p>\n</blockquote>\n","prev":{"title":"『并行计算』体系结构基础","link":"2023/06/18/『并行计算』体系结构基础"},"next":{"title":"『TVM』概述：设计与架构","link":"2023/06/12/『TVM』概述：设计与架构"},"plink":"https://gwokhiujin.github.io/2023/06/17/『中端优化』Tree-Height-Balancing-树高平衡/","toc":[{"id":"引言","title":"引言","index":"1"},{"id":"算法设计","title":"算法设计","index":"2"},{"id":"具体实现","title":"具体实现","index":"3"},{"id":"运行实例","title":"运行实例","index":"4"}],"reward":true,"copyright":{"author":"Gwok Hiujin","link":"<a href=\"https://gwokhiujin.github.io/2023/06/17/『中端优化』Tree-Height-Balancing-树高平衡/\" title=\"『中端优化』Tree-Height Balancing: 树高平衡\">https://gwokhiujin.github.io/2023/06/17/『中端优化』Tree-Height-Balancing-树高平衡/</a>","license":"Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International (<a href=\\\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/\\\" rel=\\\"external nofollow\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)","published":"June 17, 2023","updated":"June 17, 2023"},"reading_time":"3069 words in 15 min"}